      "description": "Add a SECOND layout (a 64x64 grid) under Layouts — two layouts now live under one container. buildState re-runs; the pipeline must still render. (Both grids share the 0..63 coordinate box, so the Layer buffer stays 64x64 — see the scenario NOTE.)",
